AP209 Viewer

  • This is an example of visualizing a STEP AP209 finite element model. The visualization was generated by the NIST STEP File Analyzer and rendered with X3DOM. The finite element model was generated from one of the NIST CAD models.
  • Use the mouse to rotate, pan, and zoom. Use Page Down to switch between perspective and orthographic views.
